high_descs: Go forward to the table.
Take the knife on the pan from the table.
Stay at the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right to the table.
Put the knife on the mug on the table.
Go back in front of the lettuce.
Take a slice of lettuce from the table.
Go right, go forward to the left side of the sink.
Wash the lettuce in the sink. Take the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around, go forward to the wall, turn right to the table.
Put the lettuce to the right of the mug on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Step forward to face the wooden table.
Pick up the knife on the wooden table.
Look down to face the lettuce on the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Take a step to the left and look down to face
Place the knife on the table.
Step to the right to face the lettuce on the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk forward to face the sink.
Wash the lettuce slice in the sink and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and turn right to face the table.
Place the lettuce slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: TO wash a slice of lettuce and place it on the table.

high_descs: Go straight to the table
Grab the knife off of the table
Look down at the table
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices
Move slightly to the left
Put the knife on the table
Move slightly to the right
Grab a slice of lettuce off of the table
Turn right and go to the sink
Wash the sliced lettuce in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and go to the left side of the table
Put the sliced lettuce on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting clean sliced lettuce on the table
